                  <span class="">The survey on which the work was based was carried out in 1963, after a preliminary survey by extended interview and ethnographic observationďź&OElig;on a sample of 692 subjects (both sexes) in Paris, Lille and a small provincial town. To obtain a sample large enough to make it possible to analyse variations in practices and opinions in relation to sufficiently ho mogeneous social units, a complementary ...</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2014-03-30 10:39</span>
                  
