              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>...the dominant definition of the legitimate way of appropriating culture and works of art favors those who have had early access to legitimate culture, in a cultured household, outside of scholastic disciplines, since even within the educational system it devalues scholarly knowledge and interpretation as 'scholastic' or even 'pedantic' in favor of direct experience and simple delight.</q></blockquote><div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







